Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.43,0:00:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.81,0:00:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always had the devil's luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And since when do you work\Nwith Peil Technologies, Bel?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.82,0:00:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I had... no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.40,0:00:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're the one\Ncarrying on the Vanadis legacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.61,0:00:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The machine called Aerial...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.41,0:00:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way you built it on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.58,0:00:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why have your own daughter pilot it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.29,0:00:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're much more talkative than I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.55,0:00:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use taking revenge\Nfor a 21-year-old--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.15,0:00:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That Gundam pilot...\NHow many have there been?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.18,0:00:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to see you after so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.48,0:00:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Until we meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.77,0:00:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.86,0:00:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The witch is under the wing of\NPeil Technologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected, we smoked her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.32,0:00:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.11,0:01:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. Aerial will surely win.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.33,0:01:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I trust my darling daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.88,0:02:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,"How you annoy me," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.05,0:02:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would the Ice Prince speak so harshly?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.80,0:02:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He's such a creep!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't he the one who invited you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.67,0:02:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Now he's even pissed me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.27,0:02:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because I asked about his birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.71,0:02:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You did nothing wrong, Suletta.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:03:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say you fall for people's\Nsweet words too easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.39,0:03:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Miorine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.98,0:03:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you can't take it back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.26,0:03:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Better just crush him in that duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.85,0:03:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What I can't accept is
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that you agreed to duel him\Nwithout even consulting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.10,0:03:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.29,0:03:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive you if you lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The Jeturk company is hereby\Ncutting off all your support.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.38,0:03:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course,\Nyou'll have to leave Jeturk House.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.89,0:03:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they really evicting Mr. Guel?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a direct order from the CEO.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.14,0:03:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I supposed to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a message from your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.46,0:03:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,"Consider it an act of mercy that I'm\Nat least paying the rest of your tuition."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.54,0:03:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.58,0:03:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Lauda.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Look after Jeturk House.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.69,0:04:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Both parties, deposit\Nyour souls on Libra's scales.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.38,0:04:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The duelists are Elan Ceres\Nand Suletta Mercury.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The location will be\Nthe airspace outside the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Outside the front?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.39,0:04:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Elan Ceres, what is your stake in this duel?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If I win,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.42,0:04:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Aerial will be mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.44,0:04:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Suletta Mercury, what is your stake?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we take it that you have\Nnothing to gain from this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.14,0:04:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Just decide by the day of the duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't mind, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.81,0:04:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.53,0:04:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,His walls are even higher than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.78,0:04:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you do something to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.36,0:04:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean it's my fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.34,0:04:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But since you arrived, both Guel and Elan\Nhaven't been themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.13,0:04:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I want to know more about you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.56,0:04:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mercurian Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:05:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Airspace outside the front?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you even have a thruster unit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Peil House's machines\Nare known for their mobility!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.68,0:05:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that, you're facing a new model.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.77,0:05:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be at a disadvantage\Nwith this equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.52,0:05:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.57,0:05:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The conditions of the duel are decided\Nexclusively by the Dueling Committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.96,0:05:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.53,0:05:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This House has no money\Nto buy a thruster unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.13,0:05:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we borrow one from another House?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.04,0:05:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Fat chance getting Spacians\Nto loan one to us Earthians.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.29,0:05:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we make one, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.98,0:05:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,All clear! Bring it on down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.44,0:05:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we start by inspecting\Nthe propulsion system?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.24,0:05:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Will this thing work?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.68,0:05:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate Nika.\NThere's no doubt she can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:06:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Given our finances, this is\Nputting us in a huge deficit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.83,0:06:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How are we gonna eat next month?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We're betting everything we have on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.03,0:06:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The odds are 2.7 to 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.24,0:06:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If we win, we'll cover her costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A-And if I lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.76,0:06:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Bankruptcy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.76,0:06:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Bankruptcy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.89,0:06:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll... do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.49,0:06:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You were moaning in your sleep again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't interfere with the tests.\NHow are the results?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.12,0:06:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You should have no problem\Nin your next battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.08,0:06:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean I won't survive the one after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:07:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while... Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.54,0:07:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,As gloomy as ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.84,0:07:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're my surrogate, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.10,0:07:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you act a bit more cheerfully?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Elan, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.14,0:07:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to pay my respects to you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.05,0:07:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to duel the Holder, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.07,0:07:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The company ordered me to.\NIt wasn't my idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.49,0:07:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.06,0:07:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something in it for you, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get us the bride,\Nwe'll give your face back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.28,0:07:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll also arrange for a citizen ID number.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.86,0:07:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why did you accept\Nthe role of my double?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.97,0:07:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew full well\Nthat this mobile suit was a curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.97,0:07:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Long before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.60,0:07:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I was already cursed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.89,0:07:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next we'll try a variable thrust test.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.73,0:07:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once you stop the engines,\Nreactivate immediately.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.83,0:07:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.99,0:08:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay. Your propulsion is stable.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.45,0:08:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The combustion control\Nfunctions are working, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.90,0:08:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we head back, Suletta?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.52,0:08:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.75,0:08:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomorrow...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.90,0:08:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.92,0:08:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Will you be ready to fight? With Mr. Elan...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.53,0:08:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mr. Elan was only kind to me...\Nbecause that was his plan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.06,0:08:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And yet, I was really happy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel so dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.85,0:08:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Exactly. It was dumb.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.02,0:08:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, Elan's right about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.63,0:08:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.37,0:08:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ms. Miorine...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.01,0:08:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that's just how you are.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.78,0:08:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You annoy me by meddling in my affairs{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.85,0:08:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and act on your own\Nwithout listening to me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.04,0:08:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Move forward, gain two, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So how could you run away here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:08:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no time to feel sorry for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.78,0:09:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out there and move forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.23,0:09:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.51,0:09:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm on my way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.81,0:09:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.31,0:09:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You've already forgiven her, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.85,0:09:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If she loses,\NI'll be in trouble as her bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.38,0:09:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That goes for all of you as well, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.40,0:09:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I have faith that Suletta will win.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.12,0:09:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! What the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,M-My apologies!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.31,0:09:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to be a bother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.69,0:09:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mercurian girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.90,0:09:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The duel isn't today!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Um...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.84,0:09:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is Mr. Elan there?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.26,0:09:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is LP041, Suletta Mercury.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.18,0:09:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I came...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.74,0:09:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to talk to Mr. Elan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.65,0:09:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.04,0:09:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,To Elan Ceres?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.42,0:09:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.31,0:09:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He hardly talks to us, his housemates.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.73,0:10:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody at Peil House knows a thing\Nabout that "Pharact" machine, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.32,0:10:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.78,0:10:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I really would like to talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.56,0:10:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Testing... testing...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.87,0:10:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mr. Elan, can you hear me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.90,0:10:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's Suletta!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mr. Elan!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.61,0:10:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why did you say that to me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.94,0:10:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why do we have to duel?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What do you want with Aerial?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.93,0:10:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do I really annoy you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.75,0:10:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}See? We told you so.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.89,0:10:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now go home!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.94,0:10:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Happy birthday to you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.29,0:11:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Happy birthday, happy birthday...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.97,0:11:08.73,OS,,0,0,0,,CALL FROM ELAN
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.73,0:11:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.07,0:11:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, I don't have a birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.42,0:11:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What if we made today your birthday?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.39,0:11:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you feel empty without a birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.30,0:11:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.01,0:11:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You really do...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,annoy me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.31,0:11:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Open Gate No. 6!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.91,0:11:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No anomalies in\Ncatapult superconductive storage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.27,0:11:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No error warnings\Non any components of the flight unit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.65,0:11:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No problems with INS alignment!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.71,0:11:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Suletta?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.75,0:11:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Were you able to speak with Mr. Elan?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No. But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.55,0:11:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I did decide what my stake is in this duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:12:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No obstacles in launch direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.29,0:12:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We're ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.30,0:12:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Opening hatch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.88,0:12:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Transferring launch authorization to pilot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go get him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.83,0:12:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.71,0:12:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,LP041, Suletta Mercury...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.65,0:12:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Aerial, taking off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.95,0:12:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No problems with effective exhaust velocity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.59,0:12:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Suletta,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.67,0:12:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Peil House's academic vessel\Nis ahead on your course.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No hazardous objects\Nincluding interplanetary matter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.76,0:12:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ready to launch.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.51,0:12:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Transferring authorization to pilot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.14,0:12:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,KP002, Elan Ceres...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Pharact, launching.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.35,0:12:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.88,0:12:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeturk House's new leader,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.86,0:12:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Lauda Neill.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.47,0:12:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We can skip the formalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Please just start the duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? Are you still sore\Nabout that last duel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.84,0:13:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With mutual consent by both parties,\Nwe will now begin the duel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.34,0:13:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As always, victory will go{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to the first one to break the blade\Nantenna of their opponent's mobile suit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The observer shall be the leader\Nof Grassley House, Shaddiq Zenelli.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.33,0:13:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Both parties, face off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Elan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.72,0:13:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mercurian Miss,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.88,0:13:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}have you decided\Nwhat your stake is in this duel?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.79,0:13:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, if I win,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want Mr. Elan to tell me all about himself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.27,0:13:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? That sounds like...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.05,0:13:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A love confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.37,0:13:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She's really an annoying girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.29,0:13:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.87,0:13:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Victory is never decided\Nby mobile suit performance alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.79,0:13:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Nor by the skill of the pilot, alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.71,0:13:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The result itself is the only truth!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.71,0:13:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}The result itself is the only truth!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.55,0:13:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Fix release.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Nika, this is amazing. At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.66,0:14:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Machine load is within acceptable limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice work, Nika.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.61,0:14:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.45,0:14:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to know about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.63,0:14:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a disposable pawn created\Nfor the Gundam's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.84,0:14:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that enough for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're more mean-spirited than I thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.31,0:14:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Suletta Mercury!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You have everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.10,0:14:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Friends, family...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.45,0:14:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A past and a future...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.88,0:14:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A wish list of things to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.85,0:14:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Even hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Elan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.65,0:14:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why can't you spare me this victory?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.41,0:14:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.94,0:14:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just too unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.46,0:14:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Aerial!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.66,0:15:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Elan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.84,0:15:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen you so worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What mobility!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.45,0:15:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's way too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.66,0:15:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why they chose\Nthe airspace outside the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.06,0:15:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll never keep up\Nusing a flight unit we threw together!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.50,0:15:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.62,0:15:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll torture her to death from out of range.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.50,0:15:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.94,0:15:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if she does manage to get close,\Nnext he'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Permet score,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,three.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.63,0:15:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.23,0:15:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If any of them touch her,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.54,0:15:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,even through her armor,\Nher electrical systems will be blown.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.08,0:15:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Suletta, evade it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.88,0:15:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She's hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.60,0:15:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That GUND-Bit is finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.43,0:15:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She's better at controlling\NGUND-Bits than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.77,0:16:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,In a contest of speed, a Peil mobile\Nsuit will always have the advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.64,0:16:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.92,0:16:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Suletta Mercury...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.45,0:16:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't catch him at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.77,0:16:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.18,0:16:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me your strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.91,0:16:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The Aerial has sped up, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.98,0:16:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,They're playing chase, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Her annoying behavior\Nis as tough as the hardest alloys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.29,0:16:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Permet score, four!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.65,0:16:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She's really pushing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.58,0:16:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She's forcing it too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.25,0:16:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But she's definitely getting closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:16:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Rouji?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.38,0:17:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They've passed the border lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The data storm has exceeded\Nacceptable limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.12,0:17:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Deploy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.76,0:17:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.54,0:17:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Suletta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.08,0:17:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There's damage\Nto the flight unit's left wing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Belmeria Winston...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.04,0:17:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Your diagnosis missed the mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.61,0:17:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But even so,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.25,0:17:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll at least deny your worth,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Suletta Mercury!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of there, Suletta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She's trapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.01,0:18:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing's moving. What did she do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.82,0:18:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.26,0:18:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.26,0:18:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.25,0:18:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.25,0:18:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}She did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.55,0:18:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get a record of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.26,0:18:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Permet decoding data, recording complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.09,0:18:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.82,0:18:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Good work, Aerial.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.47,0:18:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I could hear your voice\Nmore than ever today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.07,0:19:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Elan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.09,0:19:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.59,0:19:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I never knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.28,0:19:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Elan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.97,0:19:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Elan! Mr. Elan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.14,0:19:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Elan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.23,0:19:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Elan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.03,0:19:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.28,0:19:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.94,0:19:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Your stake was to learn about me, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.82,0:19:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I did have someone. Long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.78,0:19:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who would celebrate my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.74,0:19:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All this time, I thought I had nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But... it wasn't true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.08,0:20:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't true!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.50,0:20:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got it all wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.07,0:20:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.20,0:20:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There are people who will celebrate\Nyour birthday. I'm one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.30,0:20:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's absolutely wrong to say\Nyou have nothing, Mr. Elan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.27,0:20:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true. I've had it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.48,0:20:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an understanding bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.78,0:20:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tolerate... some minor two-timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.51,0:20:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He's late!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.50,0:20:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not even the meeting time yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.13,0:21:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He should be 5 minutes early!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.73,0:21:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Miorine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.45,0:21:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.01,0:21:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you... very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.86,0:21:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Just obey your curfew, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.49,0:21:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Ms. Nugen!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.30,0:21:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Number Four is experienced!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.81,0:21:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We could always choose\Nto feed back the duel data--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.65,0:21:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,An enhanced person who can't\Ncarry out their orders has no future.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.84,0:21:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You should understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.20,0:21:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We still have spares.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.76,0:21:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare the next one promptly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.06,0:21:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.77,0:21:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.37,0:21:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.70,0:22:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.49,0:22:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.13,0:22:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.94,0:22:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be here soon, Mr. Elan?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.83,0:23:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next time on {\i0}\NMobile Suit Gundam: The Witch from Mercury,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.35,0:23:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Shall We Gundam?"{\i0}
